<h2>About LI Runhui</h2>

<img src="rhl.jpg" align="right" vspace="1" hspace="45">

<p>I received my BEng degree in Computer Science from School
of Computer Science and Technology, University of Science and Technology
of China(USTC). I am now a PHD candidate in the Department of Computer Science
and Engineering, Chinese University of Hong Kong. Currently, I am a 
member of Advanced Networking and System Research Laboratory. 

<p>Now I am being supervised by <a href="http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~pclee">Prof. Patrick P.C. Lee</a> and 
<a href="http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~cslui"> Prof. John C.S. Lui</a>.

<p>When in USTC, I was supervised by <a href="http://en.nhpcc.ustc.edu.cn/Peoples_9/201107/t20110701_115017.html">Prof. Yinlong Xu</a>.

